(30, 'Aifu Resort El Montazah', 'alexandria', 'https://www.etltravel.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/aifu-resort-el-montazah-alexandria-16-1.jpg', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-s/06/f9/70/0f/aifu-resort-el-montazah.jpg', 'Aifu Resort El Montazah offers comfortable accommodation with views of Montazah Royal Gardens and the Mediterranean Sea. The hotel features cozy rooms, a restaurant, an outdoor pool, and easy access to the beach. Guests can enjoy the relaxing ambiance and beautiful surroundings. It\'s a great choice for a peaceful getaway. The hotel provides essential services for a pleasant stay. Family-friendly amenities ensure a welcoming atmosphere. Experience comfort and convenience at Aifu Resort El Montazah.', '$60 - $150 per night', 'https://www.booking.com/hotel/eg/aifu-resort.html'),
(31, 'Sofitel Winter Palace Luxor', 'luxor', 'https://www.ahstatic.com/photos/1661_rotwags_00_p_1024x768.jpg', 'https://phgcdn.com/images/uploads/LXRSW/masthead/LXRSW-masthead-egypt-ofitelwinterpalaceluxor.jpg', 'Sofitel Winter Palace Luxor is a historic hotel located on the banks of the Nile River. This grand hotel boasts lush gardens, an outdoor swimming pool, and elegant rooms and suites with modern amenities. Guests can enjoy fine dining at the hotel\'s restaurants, offering a mix of international and local cuisine. The hotel also features a spa, providing relaxing treatments and therapies. With its rich history and luxurious ambiance, Sofitel Winter Palace Luxor is an ideal choice for travelers seeking a regal experience in Luxor.', '$150 - $400 per night', 'https://www.booking.com/hotel/eg/winter-palace-luxor.html'),
(32, 'Hilton Luxor Resort & Spa', 'luxor', 'https://www.hilton.com/im/en/LUXHITW/15907967/deluxe-guest-room-king-bed-image-1.jpg?impolicy=crop&cw=5000&ch=2799&gravity=NorthWest&xposition=0&yposition=270&rw=768&rh=430', 'https://imgcy.trivago.com/c_limit,d_dummy.jpeg,f_auto,h_600,q_auto,w_600//hotelier-images/3f/ed/e25a7d62d2b26c6ac4d4ff173e036ad134fc36df2d5b570e1b3307d0b259.jpeg', 'Hilton Luxor Resort & Spa offers a luxurious stay with stunning views of the Nile River. The hotel features modern rooms and suites with contemporary decor and amenities. Guests can relax by the infinity pool, enjoy a meal at one of the several on-site restaurants, or indulge in a treatment at the full-service spa. The hotel also offers a fitness center and various activities to ensure a memorable stay. Located near Luxor\'s top attractions, Hilton Luxor Resort & Spa is perfect for both leisure and business travelers.', '$200 - $450 per night', 'https://www.booking.com/hotel/eg/hilton-luxor-resort-spa.en-gb.html'),
(33, 'Steigenberger Nile Palace Luxor', 'luxor', 'https://assets.hrewards.com/assets/562_SHR_Luxor_Nile_Palace_rooms_Executive_Suite_Panoramic_Nile_View_ec0586a976.JPG', 'https://cf.bstatic.com/xdata/images/hotel/max1024x768/524869553.jpg?k=f296b9d72f6e9ea5ed8802ef2167ce8c52ca402b2d9e5db3bdb1dbe5f991db87&o=&hp=1', 'Steigenberger Nile Palace Luxor offers a blend of luxury and comfort with its prime location along the Nile River. The hotel features spacious rooms and suites, some with balconies offering breathtaking views of the river. Guests can enjoy various dining options, including local and international cuisine. The hotel also boasts a large outdoor pool, a well-equipped fitness center, and a relaxing spa. With its close proximity to Luxor\'s ancient sites, Steigenberger Nile Palace Luxor is a perfect base for exploring the historic city.', '$180 - $420 per night', 'https://www.booking.com/hotel/eg/steigenberger-nile-palace-luxor.html'),
(34, 'Pavillon Winter Luxor', 'luxor', 'https://www.ahstatic.com/photos/1662_rokgd_00_p_1024x768.jpg', 'https://cf.bstatic.com/xdata/images/hotel/max1024x768/29220157.jpg?k=0fe416eb520efcfe96d6da04f724f201b953247a39a4673eead9526248d00164&o=&hp=1', 'Pavillon Winter Luxor is a charming hotel situated in the heart of Luxor, surrounded by lush gardens. The hotel features comfortable rooms with modern amenities and views of the garden or pool. Guests can enjoy dining at the hotel\'s restaurant, which offers a variety of dishes made from fresh, local ingredients. The outdoor pool area is perfect for relaxation, and the hotel provides easy access to Luxor\'s top attractions. With its peaceful setting and attentive service, Pavillon Winter Luxor is an excellent choice for a relaxing stay.', '$120 - $300 per night', 'https://www.booking.com/hotel/eg/new-winter-pavillon-palace.en-gb.html'),
(35, 'Jolie Ville Kings Island Luxor', 'luxor', 'https://jolievilleluxor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/home-suite.jpg', 'https://jolievilleluxor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/site-map-jolie-ville-hotel-spa-kings-island-luxor-banner.jpg', 'Jolie Ville Kings Island Luxor is a unique resort located on a private island in the Nile River. The hotel offers spacious rooms and suites with beautiful views of the river and gardens. Guests can enjoy a range of dining options, recreational activities, and amenities including multiple swimming pools, a fitness center, and a spa. The resort\'s serene setting provides a tranquil escape, while its convenient location allows for easy access to Luxor\'s historic sites. Jolie Ville Kings Island Luxor is ideal for families, couples, and solo travelers seeking a peaceful retreat.', '$130 - $350 per night', 'https://www.booking.com/hotel/eg/jolie-ville-kings-island-luxor.html'),
(36, 'Iberotel Luxor', 'luxor', 'https://cf.bstatic.com/xdata/images/hotel/max1024x768/333394387.jpg?k=95e3e98ad8a3350fdae1de843538d83ccb3c2ea5211259f0a000648765ec4a7c&o=&hp=1', 'https://cf.bstatic.com/xdata/images/hotel/max1024x768/334702813.jpg?k=b644520a99b602a9b8c5c2c8ae99ab2fee8621433536b0883ff8a023be79ae9b&o=&hp=1', 'Iberotel Luxor is a stylish hotel situated on the banks of the Nile River, offering beautiful views and comfortable accommodations. The hotel features modern rooms with amenities such as free Wi-Fi and satellite TV. Guests can enjoy a variety of dining options, relax by the outdoor swimming pool, and take advantage of the fitness center. The hotel\'s convenient location provides easy access to Luxor\'s historical sites and attractions. With its blend of comfort and convenience, Iberotel Luxor is an excellent choice for travelers visiting the ancient city.', '$100 - $220 per night', 'https://www.booking.com/hotel/eg/iberotel-luxor.html'),
(37, 'Achti Resort Luxor', 'luxor', 'https://assets.hrewards.com/assets/SHR_Resort_Achti_room_superior_Gardentwin_019c4a8c7a.jpg', 'https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/proxy/NzPwTMjLb1UMUKPnh-IZVCBzo2hTKKnGKZAv-Hgh3W8UqkVmvs4TC2Nrfbn-GR8WaWrWeKYiNvEOEwQnrJT9gD0xNh03kCdCLTBbHVwgVFsEzf5O8_RCOa5GIuU6QgwylAsZooLDPL8SZlpvdO3uVkM1sug2q0zpt4Bwvg6YcdZ5PkBuvxMqhxSl6g', 'Achti Resort Luxor is a luxurious resort offering stunning views of the Nile River and the surrounding landscape. The resort features spacious rooms and suites with modern decor and amenities. Guests can enjoy a variety of dining options, relax by the outdoor pools, and unwind at the spa. The resort also provides a range of activities and excursions to explore Luxor\'s historical sites. With its beautiful setting and excellent service, Achti Resort Luxor is an ideal destination for a memorable stay.', '$160 - $380 per night', 'https://www.booking.com/hotel/eg/sheraton-luxor-resort.html'),
(38, 'Sonesta St. George Hotel - Convention Center', 'luxor', 'https://cf.bstatic.com/xdata/images/hotel/max1024x768/389388493.jpg?k=3b5671d9e1bbdbb8e5a1137d62ada03c868db85012697f1100a12255642894d2&o=&hp=1', 'https://az712897.vo.msecnd.net/images/full/a88771a3-ad7a-4f7f-9a3a-f90ff8c0ac2b.jpeg', 'Sonesta St. George Hotel - Convention Center is a luxury hotel located on the banks of the Nile River in Luxor. The hotel offers elegant rooms and suites with contemporary furnishings and modern amenities. Guests can enjoy fine dining at the hotel\'s restaurants, relax at the outdoor pool, and rejuvenate at the spa. The hotel also features a convention center with state-of-the-art facilities, making it an ideal choice for business travelers. With its prime location and exceptional service, Sonesta St. George Hotel is perfect for both leisure and business stays.', '$170 - $390 per night', 'https://www.booking.com/hotel/eg/sonesta-st-george-luxor.html'),
(39, 'Aracan Eatabe Luxor Hotel', 'luxor', 'https://cf.bstatic.com/xdata/images/hotel/max1024x768/185992191.jpg?k=69dbab60f625b00a3d7c01c4310d402a204055bc68097372c82ffa044c9343d1&o=&hp=1', 'https://eatabe-luxor-hotel.hotelmix.fr/data/Photos/OriginalPhoto/9137/913709/913709596/Aracan-Eatabe-Luxor-Hotel-Exterior.JPEG', 'Aracan Eatabe Luxor Hotel is a comfortable and affordable hotel situated in the heart of Luxor, close to the Nile River and major attractions. The hotel features cozy rooms with modern amenities, an outdoor swimming pool, and a variety of dining options. Guests can relax in the lush garden, enjoy a drink at the bar, and explore the nearby historical sites. With its convenient location and friendly service, Aracan Eatabe Luxor Hotel is a great choice for travelers looking for a budget-friendly stay.', '$80 - $200 per night', 'https://www.booking.com/hotel/eg/el-luxor.html'),
(40, 'Mercure Luxor Karnak', 'luxor', 'https://mercure-luxor-karnak-hotel.albooked.com/data/Photos/OriginalPhoto/10808/1080855/1080855247/Mercure-Luxor-Karnak-Exterior.JPEG', 'https://gtieg.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/murcure_luxor_gti-1170x350.jpg', 'Mercure Luxor Karnak is a beautiful hotel located near the Karnak Temple, offering stunning views of the Nile River. The hotel features well-appointed rooms with modern amenities, an outdoor swimming pool, and a variety of dining options. Guests can enjoy the fitness center, relax at the spa, and take part in various recreational activities. The hotel\'s tranquil setting and excellent service make it a perfect choice for a relaxing and enjoyable stay in Luxor.', '$110 - $250 per night', 'https://ar.trivago.com/en-145/oar/hotel-mercure-luxor-karnak?search=100-13843'),
(41, 'Nefertiti Hotel Luxor', 'luxor', 'https://dynamic-media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/0d/24/31/77/nefertiti-hotel.jpg?w=700&h=-1&s=1', 'https://cf.bstatic.com/xdata/images/hotel/max1024x768/284968201.jpg?k=f859e9e8a5b2eb9afed96f8e5d7a7226c568a871d4078e13ddd65696b3753265&o=&hp=1', 'Nefertiti Hotel Luxor is a budget-friendly hotel located in the heart of Luxor, close to the Luxor Temple and other major attractions. The hotel offers comfortable rooms with modern amenities and free Wi-Fi. Guests can enjoy meals at the rooftop restaurant, which provides stunning views of the Nile River and Luxor Temple. The hotel also offers a variety of services including tour arrangements, bike rentals, and a 24-hour front desk. With its central location and friendly atmosphere, Nefertiti Hotel Luxor is a great choice for budget-conscious travelers.', '$40 - $100 per night', 'https://www.booking.com/hotel/eg/nefertiti.html'),
(42, 'Sofitel Legend Old Cataract Aswan', 'aswan', 'https://cf.bstatic.com/xdata/images/hotel/max1024x768/326740552.jpg?k=41358df4e13a8938f2586a9a55083f37fcc46af4c3f1547be7d3e0ba6ad4a0c8&o=&hp=1', 'https://cf.bstatic.com/xdata/images/hotel/max1024x768/326740587.jpg?k=aafdb507795e1bc36813c03ae1cf292effa278e4f2de1bb413d63d8f73eb1cb6&o=&hp=1', 'Sofitel Legend Old Cataract Aswan is a historic luxury hotel located on the banks of the Nile River. The hotel features elegant rooms and suites with modern amenities and stunning views. Guests can enjoy fine dining at the hotel\'s restaurants, relax by the outdoor pool, or indulge in a treatment at the spa. The hotel also offers a fitness center and beautiful gardens. With its rich history and luxurious ambiance, Sofitel Legend Old Cataract Aswan is a perfect choice for a lavish stay in Aswan.', '$300 - $600 per night', 'https://www.booking.com/hotel/eg/sohitel-legend-old-cataract.html'),
(43, 'Movenpick Resort Aswan', 'aswan', 'https://m.ahstatic.com/is/image/accorhotels/Aswan_xxxxxxxxxxxx_i120697:3by2?wid=364&hei=243&dpr=on,2.625&qlt=75&resMode=sharp2&op_usm=0.5,0.3,2,0&iccEmbed=true&icc=sRGB', 'https://cdn.adventure-life.com/29/55/56/f2/663x400.webp', 'Movenpick Resort Aswan is a luxurious hotel located on Elephantine Island, offering panoramic views of the Nile River. The hotel features spacious rooms and suites with modern amenities, multiple dining options, and a rooftop restaurant. Guests can relax by the outdoor pool, enjoy a variety of recreational activities, and take advantage of the fitness center. The hotel also provides easy access to Aswan\'s top attractions, making it an ideal choice for both leisure and business travelers.', '$250 - $500 per night', 'https://www.booking.com/hotel/eg/movenpick-resort-aswan.html'),
(44, 'Basma Hotel Aswan', 'aswan', 'https://cf.bstatic.com/xdata/images/hotel/max1024x768/273724229.jpg?k=3eb6c972ecc00c1e24d3df7536bebabc760ee940b1b2cc8c69e37f67305a108e&o=&hp=1', 'https://cf.bstatic.com/xdata/images/hotel/max1024x768/273965927.jpg?k=b85de18353eeb479b554ee84faea768fea2888e2e3d4c1b765654761eb3d710a&o=&hp=1', 'Basma Hotel Aswan is a comfortable hotel located on the highest hill in Aswan, offering stunning views of the Nile River and the city. The hotel features well-appointed rooms with modern amenities, an outdoor swimming pool, and a variety of dining options. Guests can relax in the lush gardens, enjoy a drink at the bar, and explore the nearby attractions. With its beautiful setting and friendly service, Basma Hotel Aswan is a great choice for a relaxing stay.', '$100 - $200 per night', 'https://www.booking.com/hotel/eg/basma-aswan.html'),
(45, 'Pyramisa Isis Island Aswan Resort', 'aswan', 'https://dynamic-media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/1a/cb/e4/8d/pyramisa-isis-island.jpg?w=700&h=-1&s=1', 'https://cf.bstatic.com/xdata/images/hotel/max1024x768/510651158.jpg?k=66355631ac6a89306a7d0db92728a13777e9bb2f567035b3077243eae547aea5&o=&hp=1', 'Pyramisa Isis Island Aswan Resort is a luxurious hotel located on a private island in the Nile River. The resort features spacious rooms and suites with modern amenities and balconies overlooking the river. Guests can enjoy a variety of dining options, relax by the multiple swimming pools, and indulge in treatments at the spa. The resort also offers a fitness center, tennis courts, and a range of recreational activities. With its tranquil setting and excellent facilities, Pyramisa Isis Island Aswan Resort is ideal for a peaceful getaway.', '$150 - $350 per night', 'https://www.booking.com/hotel/eg/lti-pyramisa-isis-island-aswan.html'),
(46, 'Tolip Aswan Hotel', 'aswan', 'https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/proxy/VGqpsi-2b0oXK1OhY-awGwGZQgwGKebYPWw0ixgoC0Qa9lQW1K98JgJ4BjNzpQiJmvjXF96uGmNO0ClBANZ0', 'https://cf.bstatic.com/xdata/images/hotel/max500/288782500.jpg?k=1ac589eee7a3d83ef2e8abe567e483f58bd28aa265073f19410ddebfd7bfffd2&o=&hp=1', 'Tolip Aswan Hotel is a modern hotel situated on the banks of the Nile River, offering comfortable accommodations and excellent amenities. The hotel features well-appointed rooms with contemporary decor and free Wi-Fi. Guests can enjoy dining at the hotel\'s restaurants, relax by the outdoor pool, and take advantage of the fitness center and spa. The hotel\'s convenient location provides easy access to Aswan\'s attractions, making it a perfect choice for both leisure and business travelers.', '$120 - $250 per night', 'https://www.booking.com/hotel/eg/helnan-aswan-formerly-iberotel-aswan.html'),
(47, 'Keylany Hotel', 'aswan', 'https://images.trvl-media.com/lodging/17000000/16330000/16320100/16320029/3459d278.jpg?impolicy=resizecrop&rw=575&rh=575&ra=fill', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-s/01/29/60/a9/keylany-hotel-front-door.jpg', 'Keylany Hotel is a budget-friendly hotel located in the heart of Aswan, close to the Nile River and major attractions. The hotel offers comfortable rooms with modern amenities and free Wi-Fi. Guests can enjoy meals at the rooftop restaurant, which provides stunning views of the city and the Nile. The hotel also offers a variety of services including tour arrangements, bike rentals, and a 24-hour front desk. With its central location and friendly atmosphere, Keylany Hotel is a great choice for budget-conscious travelers.', '$30 - $70 per night', 'https://ar.trivago.com/en-145/oar/hotel-keylany-assuan-aswan?search=100-86760'),
(48, 'Nile Hotel Aswan', 'aswan', 'https://cf.bstatic.com/xdata/images/hotel/max1024x768/184006712.jpg?k=5da37e44fc67b97a99562f59fcff0f3c4af716a644812b362cb095d533ceb380&o=&hp=1', 'https://cf.bstatic.com/xdata/images/hotel/max1280x900/183993208.jpg?k=045ccb03e8cf95d139610c1ee617e48848fe39e6bfc2a7cd342791d34bd41c84&o=&hp=1', 'Nile Hotel Aswan is a comfortable hotel located on the banks of the Nile River, offering beautiful views and modern amenities. The hotel features well-appointed rooms with free Wi-Fi and satellite TV. Guests can enjoy dining at the hotel\'s restaurant, relax by the outdoor pool, and take advantage of the fitness center. The hotel\'s convenient location provides easy access to Aswan\'s attractions, making it a perfect choice for both leisure and business travelers.', '$50 - $120 per night', 'https://www.booking.com/hotel/eg/pyramisa-isis-corniche-aswan-resort.html'),
(49, 'Hapi Hotel', 'aswan', 'https://www.etltravel.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/hapi-hotel-aswan-egypt-6-1.jpg', 'https://cf.bstatic.com/xdata/images/hotel/max500/107923416.jpg?k=ca1863c4837624635bc809ad946fb549647692ed2f85c5e28316e2df6bd3a4d1&o=&hp=1', 'Hapi Hotel is a modern hotel located in the center of Aswan, close to the Nile River and major attractions. The hotel features comfortable rooms with contemporary decor and amenities such as free Wi-Fi and flat-screen TVs. Guests can enjoy a variety of dining options, relax in the lounge, and explore the nearby attractions. With its convenient location and friendly service, Hapi Hotel is a great choice for travelers looking for a comfortable and affordable stay.', '$40 - $100 per night', 'https://www.booking.com/hotel/eg/happi.html'),
(50, 'Ekadolli Nubian Guesthouse', '', 'https://cf.bstatic.com/xdata/images/hotel/max1024x768/13057954.jpg?k=b4c703d542b0f2ea425d48de47eb52a270a370fe53599be3b7cd36e8097abc26&o=&hp=1', 'https://content.skyscnr.com/available/581470681/581470681_WxH.jpg', 'Ekadolli Nubian Guesthouse is a traditional Nubian guesthouse located in the village of Gharb Soheil, offering a unique cultural experience. The guesthouse features comfortable rooms with modern amenities and traditional Nubian decor. Guests can enjoy home-cooked meals, relax in the garden, and explore the surrounding area. The guesthouse also offers various activities and excursions, providing an authentic Nubian experience. With its warm hospitality and cultural charm, Ekadolli Nubian Guesthouse is a great choice for travelers seeking an authentic stay in Aswan.', '$20 - $50 per night', 'https://www.booking.com/hotel/eg/ekadolli-nubian-guesthouse-aswan.html'),
(51, 'Sunrise Arabian Beach Resort', 'sharm', 'https://i.pinimg.com/originals/01/93/e1/0193e1101205aaa6c1f1ff1703495b6d.jpg', 'https://th.bing.com/th/id/R.3b9628c774c0f9d751f9a0a6cfd078ed?rik=fbE6Bqd2YUlpQw&pid=ImgRaw&r=0', 'Sunrise Arabian Beach Resort is a luxurious resort located in the heart of Sharm El Sheikh. The resort features elegant rooms and suites, each with stunning views of the Red Sea. Guests can enjoy a variety of international cuisines at the multiple on-site restaurants. The resort offers numerous activities, including snorkeling, diving, and water sports. Relax by the expansive pools or indulge in a treatment at the full-service spa. The resort\'s beautiful gardens and private beach make it a perfect destination for both relaxation and adventure. With its world-class amenities and exceptional service, Sunrise Arabian Beach Resort promises an unforgettable stay.', '$100 - $250 per night', 'https://www.booking.com/hotel/eg/sunrise-arabian-beach-resort.html'),
(52, 'Rixos Sharm El Sheikh', 'sharm', 'https://th.bing.com/th/id/R.748589ae60b04e31b048712f435cd293?rik=BlAlu%2bAWqtQxpw&pid=ImgRaw&r=0', 'https://il.bestattravel.co.uk/Images/Cropped/AFR-Egypt-SharmElSheikh-RixosSharmElSheikh-103588-RixosSharmAdultNight-2-RixosSharmAdultRSSAirPhotos15.jpg', 'Rixos Sharm El Sheikh is an all-inclusive resort known for its opulence and extensive facilities. Located on the picturesque Nabq Bay, the resort offers luxurious rooms and suites with private balconies. The property features numerous restaurants, offering diverse culinary experiences from around the world. Guests can enjoy an array of leisure activities, including a water park, tennis courts, and a state-of-the-art fitness center. The resort\'s private beach and coral reef make it an ideal spot for diving and snorkeling. A dedicated kids\' club ensures fun for the whole family. With its exceptional service and lavish amenities, Rixos Sharm El Sheikh provides a perfect getaway for travelers seeking luxury and adventure.', '$150 - $350 per night', 'https://www.booking.com/hotel/eg/rixos-sharm-el-sheikh.html');
